text: I wish somebody has told me that it's
okay not to have to wear a very very
nasty looking suit with a men shirt and
a bag of pearls and that's how I had to
dress put the same intensity into having
a life outside of work seek out mentors
10 12 years your senior lean in have
confidence in yourself and be willing to
put forth a point of view early and
often I wish somebody has told me that I
should just stay being ambitious and not
justify in my head why I had to do X
versus y I should just be who I am and
being ambitious is who I am understand
in your heart what you really want to be
doing and go for it there are all
different kinds of intelligence and that
I would try to encourage people to
appreciate that intelligence and to lead
from the heart I think that the best
piece of advice nobody gave this to me
but I think is just to come in with a
fully fully open open mind and a great
sense of humor
